      "data": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>This functions like a regular @Compendium[pf2e.equipment-srd.T8EopYZLT137CsdW]{Net}, except the escape DC is equal to the Clockwork Librarian's Crafting DC [[25]]. The Clockwork Librarian does not need to use an action to draw a net; it can launch one of its five nets from its shoulder&nbsp; immediately.</p>\n<p>Make a ranged attack roll against a Medium or smaller creature within 20 feet. On a hit, the target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.AJh5ex99aV6VTggg]{Flat-Footed} and takes a -10- foot circumstance penalty to its Speeds until it @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.SkZAQRkLLkmBQNB9]{Escapes}, and on a critical hit, it's also @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.eIcWbB5o3pP6OIMe]{Immobilized}until it Escapes. The Escape DC is 25. A creature adjacent to the target can Interact to remove the net.</p>\n<p>{{actor.data.name}}</p>"
